        已过时。 Will become immutable.

        参数:
        newName - The referenced object's new name.

      • isDummy

        @Deprecated
 @ScheduledApiChange(when="5.0")
public boolean isDummy()
        已过时。 Dummy references are deprecated. In case of drive order destinations, use DriveOrder.Destination#Destination(org.opentcs.data.TCSObjectReference) instead.
        Returns false if this reference really references an object, or true if it's a dummy reference without a real object.
        返回:
        false if this reference really references an object, or true if it's a dummy reference without a real object.

      • clone

        public TCSObjectReference<E> clone()
        Returns a distinct copy of this reference. The clone's referent attribute is set to null to prevent the actual referenced object to be leaked outside the kernel.
        覆盖:
        clone 在类中 java.lang.Object
        返回:
        A distinct copy of this reference, with its referent attribute set to null.

        T - The type of the dummy reference to be returned.
